/** 
 * Sets the builder to generate, allocate and attach a 24 bit depth buffer to the FrameBuffer to be built. If useStencilBuffer() is also used, an 8 bit stencil buffer will also be associated with the depth buffer. For details on the specific characteristics of the buffers, see the FBO.create() method.
 * @return The calling instance, to chain calls, i.e.: new FBObuilder(...).useDepthBuffer().build();
 */
public FboConfig useDepthBuffer(){
  useDepthBuffer=true;
  return this;
}
